<br>
Now since it seems enough people can not do the right thing on their own.. we had to make laws to... enforce the right things...  I'm not saying all laws are right.. but unless a law is hurting someone... well why break it?  <br>
<br>
Can you explain to me why i should feel bad and want them to legalize a drug for recreational use?<br>
